# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .copilotignore — Hide performance-issue metadata from AI agents
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file prevents GitHub Copilot (code completions, Chat, and CLI)
# from indexing files that document intentional performance issues.
# The agentic loop should discover bottlenecks through measurement,
# not by reading hints in documentation.

# Performance-issue registry (human-only reference)
sample-api/.perf-issues.md

# Copilot analysis artifacts (prompts/responses between iterations)
sample-api/results/**/copilot-prompt.md
sample-api/results/**/copilot-response.md

# Optimization metadata (contains explicit issue descriptions)
sample-api/results/metadata/optimization-queue.md
sample-api/results/metadata/optimization-log.md

# Root cause analysis docs (contain issue descriptions from prior runs)
sample-api/results/**/root-cause.md
